Abilities:
--> Constructor now takes an ID variable
--> Ability to define non supported chips by declaring the following:

        #define CHIPSIZE X    // X has to be as follows: a 256KB (kilobit) chip would be KB256
                              // A 16MB(Megabit) chip would be MB16 etc.

--> Got rid of getChipName() - it is superfluous
